{"tid":1154411,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"送中法係咪適用中華民國既叛國罪","createTime":"2019-05-14T09:36:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-14T10:53:45.000Z","uid":65328,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"88eebcd94fa9fe2f54a6c6076b78197170928270","tid":1154411,"uid":65328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T09:36:09.000Z","msg":"送中法係咪適用中華民國既叛國罪<br />\n林鄭話送中法係因為有香港人係台灣殺咗人， 犯咗中華民國既法， <br />\n<br />\n但照中華民國既法， 大陸都係中華民國合法領土， 咁係咪可以拉所有叛國既人去台灣"},{"pid":"7d8f30fab805abdb1d289004dfd3074e15fbeaf1","tid":1154411,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T09:41:31.000Z","msg":"首先中華民國要有俾國籍你<br />\n唔係點叛國<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61a398de89d5e38b09c92e322ecf4efbdf199024","tid":1154411,"uid":33028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T09:46:10.000Z","msg":"要雙重犯罪"},{"pid":"b4f6635252e9db5c40170a746d1c0fe1bd11b0b1","tid":1154411,"uid":33028,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7d8f30fab805abdb1d289004dfd3074e15fbeaf1","tid":1154411,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T09:41:31.000Z","msg":"首先中華民國要有俾國籍你<br />\n唔係點叛國<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T09:47:19.000Z","msg":"法理上中國籍香港人都有中華民國籍"},{"pid":"f5e62fa082b1abdbd448ea38973e6a74c821e5da","tid":1154411,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b4f6635252e9db5c40170a746d1c0fe1bd11b0b1","tid":1154411,"uid":33028,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7d8f30fab805abdb1d289004dfd3074e15fbeaf1","tid":1154411,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T09:41:31.000Z","msg":"首先中華民國要有俾國籍你<br />\n唔係點叛國<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T09:47:19.000Z","msg":"法理上中國籍香港人都有中華民國籍"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T09:49:13.000Z","msg":"法律上中華民國冇簽過聯合聲明<br />\n你係英藉添"},{"pid":"037d0c0393ffed3bad6432bef0d5fe145c4df60c","tid":1154411,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b4f6635252e9db5c40170a746d1c0fe1bd11b0b1","tid":1154411,"uid":33028,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7d8f30fab805abdb1d289004dfd3074e15fbeaf1","tid":1154411,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T09:41:31.000Z","msg":"首先中華民國要有俾國籍你<br />\n唔係點叛國<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T09:47:19.000Z","msg":"法理上中國籍香港人都有中華民國籍"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T09:55:32.000Z","msg":"《中華民國憲法》第三條：「具有中華民國國籍者為中華民國國民。」<br />\n<br />\n《入出國及移民法》第三條：「<span style=\"color: red;\">國民：指具有中華民國國籍之居住臺灣地區設有戶籍國民或臺灣地區無戶籍國民。</span>」<br />\n<br />\n國民身分之確認\t<br />\n《中華民國國籍法》採屬人主義，出生時父或母為中華民國國民，屬中華民國國籍。"},{"pid":"566332f0302f8200e093b8dac3c8508b5c592ca1","tid":1154411,"uid":157369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f5e62fa082b1abdbd448ea38973e6a74c821e5da","tid":1154411,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b4f6635252e9db5c40170a746d1c0fe1bd11b0b1","tid":1154411,"uid":33028,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7d8f30fab805abdb1d289004dfd3074e15fbeaf1","tid":1154411,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T09:41:31.000Z","msg":"首先中華民國要有俾國籍你<br />\n唔係點叛國<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T09:47:19.000Z","msg":"法理上中國籍香港人都有中華民國籍"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T09:49:13.000Z","msg":"法律上中華民國冇簽過聯合聲明<br />\n你係英藉添"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T09:56:08.000Z","msg":"就係因為冇談判 無聯合聲明<br />\n中華民國從來唔承認不平等條約<br />\n唔承認英國同埋葡萄牙對香港同埋澳門嘅殖民統治<br />\n所以宜家都唔會喺 BNO 同 1999年前簽發嘅葡萄牙護照上面蓋印<br />\n<br />\n中華民國國籍有分「有/無戶籍國民」<br />\n陸港澳人民屬「無戶籍國民」<br />\n中華民國有權對你發護照，但係冇身分證字號<br />\n<br />\n所以外國對中華民國嘅免簽證<br />\n講明要 有加註身分證字號的中華民國護照<br />\n即係只限係 台澎金馬有戶籍之國民"},{"pid":"29cb66a6d416dadd712e370840fda7e6abc5a5cf","tid":1154411,"uid":157369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T09:57:53.000Z","msg":"另外答返條問題<br />\n叛國罪唔喺送中條例嘅罪行列表裡面"},{"pid":"98fe9c2eacbbf07ce700e210bf8bc7a0ed446794","tid":1154411,"uid":65328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"29cb66a6d416dadd712e370840fda7e6abc5a5cf","tid":1154411,"uid":157369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T09:57:53.000Z","msg":"另外答返條問題<br />\n叛國罪唔喺送中條例嘅罪行列表裡面"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T09:59:55.000Z","msg":"支那犯既法， 係中華民國黎講都應該有相關既法"},{"pid":"f531d4dc4bcb04fc29afb5bfec111e7190629dfa","tid":1154411,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"566332f0302f8200e093b8dac3c8508b5c592ca1","tid":1154411,"uid":157369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f5e62fa082b1abdbd448ea38973e6a74c821e5da","tid":1154411,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b4f6635252e9db5c40170a746d1c0fe1bd11b0b1","tid":1154411,"uid":33028,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T09:47:19.000Z","msg":"法理上中國籍香港人都有中華民國籍"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T09:49:13.000Z","msg":"法律上中華民國冇簽過聯合聲明<br />\n你係英藉添"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T09:56:08.000Z","msg":"就係因為冇談判 無聯合聲明<br />\n中華民國從來唔承認不平等條約<br />\n唔承認英國同埋葡萄牙對香港同埋澳門嘅殖民統治<br />\n所以宜家都唔會喺 BNO 同 1999年前簽發嘅葡萄牙護照上面蓋印<br />\n<br />\n中華民國國籍有分「有/無戶籍國民」<br />\n陸港澳人民屬「無戶籍國民」<br />\n中華民國有權對你發護照，但係冇身分證字號<br />\n<br />\n所以外國對中華民國嘅免簽證<br />\n講明要 有加註身分證字號的中華民國護照<br />\n即係只限係 台澎金馬有戶籍之國民"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T10:00:40.000Z","msg":"你咁堅持咪由得你<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13ddf9b0a57778ce56418c1be52a96b3506da4b9","tid":1154411,"uid":65328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f531d4dc4bcb04fc29afb5bfec111e7190629dfa","tid":1154411,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"566332f0302f8200e093b8dac3c8508b5c592ca1","tid":1154411,"uid":157369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f5e62fa082b1abdbd448ea38973e6a74c821e5da","tid"